headline: 4 Stocks to Buy as the Leisure & Recreation Industry Looks Promising
summary: The Leisure and Recreation Products industry is benefiting from strong fitness demand and booming golf trends. Moreover, stocks like AS, POOL, GOLF and MODG are likely to benefit from the trend.

headline: 1 Safe-and-Steady Stock Worth Your Attention and 2 That Underwhelm
